    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure for describing known devices for a controller. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This contains arrays of known I3C and I2C devices.</para>
<para>This is a helper struct that can be used by controller device driver to aid in device management. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
